-- Berkshire Hathaway's General Re Life gets new CEO
-- 
-- Fri May 4, 2007 4:54pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/05/04/us-generalre-ceo-idUSWEN773220070504

 

 LOS ANGELES  (Reuters) - General Re Corp., a wholly-owned subsidiary of Berkshire Hathaway Inc. ( BRKa.N ), on Friday named Steven Mannik president and chief executive of General Re Life Corp. 

 Mannik, formerly of Manulife Financial Corp., was responsible for Manulife's Global Reinsurance operation. General Re Life Corporation specializes in reinsuring Life and Health insurance products.